title: Penny Skateboards X Christian Hosoi // Signature Model 2014
description:
Known for his raw and dynamic approach to skateboarding, Christian Hosoi brings his legendary graphic to Penny Skateboards. Continuing the success of the 2013 Hosoi board, we are now introducing the classic Hosoi "Hammerhead" graphic!


Shot & Edit by : Ryan Spencer
Track: Jungle Doctors - Better
